REQUIREMENTS:

https://github.com/spotDL/spotify-downloader
https://github.com/0x7d4/syncedlyrics
https://github.com/flyingrub/scdl


SINGLE / PlAYLIST DL-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

spotdl --output "${HOME}\Downloads\IDM\Music\" --output-format flac --search-threads 2 --download-threads 1 --lyrics-provider musixmatch "URL"

YOUTUBE W/ SPOTIFY METADATA------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

spotdl --output "${HOME}\Downloads\IDM\Music\" --output-format flac --search-threads 2 --download-threads 1 --lyrics-provider musixmatch "YouTubeURL|SpotifyURL"

SOUNDCLOUD DL--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

scdl --force-metadata --addtofile --original-art --extract-artist --onlymp3 --flac --path "${HOME}\Downloads\IDM\Music\" -l "URL"

SYNCED LYRICS SEARCH-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

cd "PATH_TO_SAVE"

syncedlyrics "[ARTIST_NAME] - [TRACK_NAME]"
